<body>
<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1040070" n="1"/> 
  <!-- Editorische Vorbemerkung wegen dem PS. des Vaters. Mit Fritz besprechen.  -->
<opener><salute>Viro Juveni Pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>stantissimo
    <lb/><rs type="person"><choice><orig>NICOLAO</orig><reg>Nicolao</reg></choice> <choice><orig>BERNOULLIO</orig><reg>Bernoullio</reg></choice></rs> <abbr>J. U. C.</abbr>
    <lb/>Consobrino Suo Carissimo</salute>
  <lb/><abbr>S. P. D.</abbr>
  <lb/><rs type="person">Benedictus Stehelius</rs>.</opener>
  <p><lb/><rs type="letter" key="B_991170517163305501">Tuas</rs>, Consobrine Optime, accepit <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-121297829">Pater</rs> meus <rs type="letter" key="B_991170517163305501">litteras</rs>
    <lb/><choice><orig><g ref="#etlig">&amp;</g></orig><reg>et</reg></choice> ex iis sane non parum l<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>titi<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> cepit, quippe
    <lb/>qui Te diligit plurimum <choice><orig><g ref="#etlig">&amp;</g></orig><reg>et</reg></choice> dilexit semper, ac de
    <lb/>pristino suo in Te amore remisisse, aliquid haud
    <lb/>velim dubites. <rs type="person">Mater</rs> <choice><orig><g ref="#etlig">&amp;</g></orig><reg>et</reg></choice> reliqui <rs type="person">Fratres</rs> <choice><orig><g ref="#etlig">&amp;</g></orig><reg>et</reg></choice> <rs type="person">Sorores</rs>
    <lb/>optime se habent, <choice><orig><g ref="#etlig">&amp;</g></orig><reg>et</reg></choice> ut felix faustum<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> sit iter quod
    <lb/><del><gap/></del>paras, optant. <rs type="letter" key="B_991170517163305501">Litteris</rs> Tuis jucundissimis
    <lb/>Ipse respondisset <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-121297829">Pater</rs>, nisi tum privata tum publica,
    <lb/>ut Tu Ipse non ignoras, Eum negotia distractum
    <lb/>haberent. Ceterum quod ad semina attinet qu<del><gap/></del><add><choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></add> Tibi
    <lb/><rs type="person">Soror</rs> Tua Carissima misit, nihil est quod gratias
    <lb/>agas, si est quod Tibi aliud officium pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>stare possit,
    <lb/>id minime recusat<del><gap/></del>. Interim sententiam
    <lb/>Tuam <rs type="person">Pater</rs> valde approbat, <choice><orig><g ref="#etlig">&amp;</g></orig><reg>et</reg></choice> Deum precatur ut
    <lb/>iter quod ingredi jamjam in animo habes, prosperum
    <lb/>ac felix reddat. Permitte<del><gap/></del> etiam<supplied>,</supplied> Consobrine suavissime<supplied>,</supplied>
    <lb/>ut <rs type="person">Patris</rs> mei Optimi votis mea etiam jungam, <del><gap/></del><add>rogans</add> ut
    <lb/>nos carissima Tua pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>sentia non diu prives, <del><gap/></del><choice><orig><g ref="#etlig">&amp;</g></orig><reg>et</reg></choice>
    <lb/>itinere hoc feliciter peracto brevi Tibi prosper<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>
    <lb/>reditum gratulemur. </p><closer><choice><orig>VALE</orig><reg>Vale</reg></choice>, Consobrine Optime. Et me
      <lb/>Ama. <dateline>Dabam <rs type="place">Basile<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> <date when="1710-04-24">8.<hi rend="sup"><hi rend="u">vo</hi></hi> <abbr>Calend.</abbr> Mai<del><gap/></del><add>j</add><choice><orig>:</orig><reg>.</reg></choice> <abbr>An<choice><orig>:</orig><reg>.</reg></choice></abbr> 1710</date>.</dateline></closer> 
  <pb facs="1040071" n="2"/>
<postscript>
  <p>Sit<note type="editorial">Das P. S. stammt von <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-121297829">Johann Heinrich Stehelin</rs>.</note> tibi eunti et redeunti Comes Salus. Viros Reverendos et Clarissimos
    <lb/><rs type="person">Malebrancium</rs> si adhuc in vivis est, et <rs type="person">Varignonium</rs> meo nomine
    <lb/>saluta. <rs type="place">Bern<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> apud <rs type="person">Fritshium</rs> venale prostat <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-100068995">Caneparii</rs> <rs type="biblio">Opus de Atramentis</rs>
    <lb/>in <abbr>4.<hi rend="sup">o</hi></abbr> <rs type="place">Venet<choice><orig>:</orig><reg>.</reg></choice></rs> ibi<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice><!-- Todo: Kontrollieren ob ibique korrekt. -->, quod si pro co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>odo pretio mihi comparare poteris, rem
    <lb/>mihi facies gratissimam. Vale iterum at<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> iterum.
    <lb/><abbr>S. T. T.</abbr><!-- ToDo: Abkürzung kontrollieren. -->
    <lb/><rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-121297829">Stehelius</rs> <abbr>Med<choice><orig>:</orig><reg>.</reg></choice></abbr></p>
</postscript>
  <pb facs="1039655" type="archival"/> <pb facs="1039653" type="archival"/>
